{"type":"article","id":13559,"title":"谈一个合并主题的问题","uid":749,"topics":[3323],"contents":"品葱是文章只能和文章合并，问题只能和问题合并<br>\n但是内容类似的文章和问题，就无法合并了<br>\n<br>\n比如我今天发了一篇文章：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/13515\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/13515</a><br>\n十几分钟前，admin告诉我，已经有了一个类似的问题：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/16950\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/question/16950</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/172701a0f80f8e7770553.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/172701a0f80f8e7770553.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/172701a0f80f8e7770553.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n但问题是，我写的是文章，另一个是问题，文章和问题无法合并。<br>\n<br>\n各位这么看这种情况？","date":"2020-02-03","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}